data.description: New Roof!!!! Discover the unique allure of this property as you step into a space adorned with floor tile throughout the entire house. Embracing 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an inviting kitchen island, the spacious layout harmoniously blends functionality with style.  Once inside, embrace the openness and lightness that welcomes you, making you feel right at home. The thoughtfully crafted floor plan seamlessly connects each area, fashioning an inviting living space ideally suited for hosting gatherings.  The contemporary kitchen stands out as the heart of the home, showcasing a chic kitchen island that effortlessly marries visual allure with practicality. Whether you're preparing family feasts or entertaining guests, this kitchen promises to make a lasting impression.  Enhancing your comfort, relish the benefits of a newly installed AC unit, ensuring optimal efficiency and tranquility since its installation a mere year ago. Additionally, anticipate the arrival of a new roof, poised to provide you with peace of mind and safeguard your investment for years to come..
